Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是南極嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到南極啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡就是南極啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好 100公斤內沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃了那麼多點心 重量居然沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你再想想點心去哪了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要搭那個去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能搭雪地車去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 怎麼一副要死了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有要死的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是好大的船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你先看看再說啊
