Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有信心跟她說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道放著不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別擔心 她可沒有生你的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是小理都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她只是有點寂寞吧
