Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別踢皮球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做了什麼怪事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實…也不是什麼怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我站在你的立場上 我也會那麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得朋友不是嘴上說說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我經常聽人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那朋友究竟是什麼？
