Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:56.32,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聽見一聲輕輕的「想見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:04.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}聲音漸漸消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:22.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:29.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白閃耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:38.52,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們踩下的足跡 漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:46.50,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以為這些時光 永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:54.77,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}卻突然畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:20:04.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這份心情 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:14.01,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何語言 都要寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:23.27,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}總有一天 會再度牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:35.32,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}帶著我們 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:46.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以這些時光 我不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:55.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度過的珍貴點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:04.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它們 會永遠牽起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:15.09,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永遠 直到永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:20.39,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「現在在上課啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在睡覺啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在考慮要不要回覆吧」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能猜到她是什麼表情 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對我而言 朋友大概就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我也不怎麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但大概就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 可能幫不上你什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}AND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 你生日之前剛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那時我們一直在暈船 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以小理提議在南極幫你過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請弓子小姐分了我們一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒做好的部分 就麻煩你用想像彌補啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹蠟燭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛見面時也是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家才沒哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不趕快吹就要融化了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…這是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有朋友幫我慶生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹吧 結月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家的第一次啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}點心時間到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
